<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-XXJ55KE2X1"></script>
    <script>
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
      gtag('js', new Date());

      gtag('config', 'G-XXJ55KE2X1');
    </script>
    
    <title>AI 官方 LINE 智能管家 - 護胰大聯盟 PANCREAS PROTECTION ALLIANCE</title>
    <meta name="description" content="護胰大聯盟官方 LINE 智能管家。收錄各大醫學中心與衛福部權威資訊，透過 AI 技術，讓您在 LINE 上隨時解答胰臟健康疑問。">

    <link rel="icon" href="images/logopng.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="images/logopng.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #3E9F8F;
            --primary-dark: #004C74;
            --primary-light: #eef7f5;
            --accent: #D4B872;
            --line-green: #06C755; /* LINE 官方品牌綠 */
        }
        
        body { background-color: #f8fafc; padding-top: 80px; font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif; }
        
        /* 導覽列設定 */
        .navbar {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08) !important;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-light);
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 1000;
        }
        .nav-container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; }
        .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; text-decoration: none; padding: 5px 0; }
        .logo-icon img { width: 48px; height: 48px; display: block; object-fit: contain; }
        .logo-text-wrapper { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; line-height: 1.1; }
        .logo-title { font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--primary-dark) !important; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 2px; }
        .logo-subtitle { font-size: 10px; color: var(--primary) !important; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; }

        .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; }
        .nav-links a.dropbtn { color: var(--primary-dark) !important; font-weight: 700; padding: 10px 15px; text-decoration: none; }
        .nav-links a.dropbtn:hover { color: var(--primary) !important; }

        /* Hero 區塊設計 (類似 App 落地頁) */
        .bot-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark) 0%, #002c44 100%);
            padding: 80px 20px;
            color: white;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        .bot-hero-container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 50px;
        }
        .bot-hero-text { flex: 1; }
        .bot-hero-text h1 { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.3; }
        .bot-hero-text h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
        .bot-hero-text p { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; color: #cbd5e1; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        
        /* QR Code 卡片 */
        .qr-card-wrapper { flex-shrink: 0; }
        .qr-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            text-align: center;
            width: 320px;
            border-top: 8px solid var(--line-green);
        }
        .qr-card img { width: 180px; height: 180px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: inline-block; }
        .qr-card h3 { color: var(--text-main); font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: 800; }
        .bot-id { background: #f1f5f9; color: var(--primary-dark); padding: 8px 15px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .btn-line-add {
            display: block;
            background-color: var(--line-green);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-line-add:hover { background-color: #05a546; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.4); }

        /* 特色說明區塊 */
        .features-section { padding: 80px 20px; background: #ffffff; }
        .features-title { text-align: center; color: var(--primary-dark); font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 50px; }
        .features-grid { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 30px; }
        .feature-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border-color: var(--primary); }
        .feature-icon { font-size: 50px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: inline-block; }
        .feature-card h3 { color: var(--primary-dark); font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 800; }
        .feature-card p { color: #64748b; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

        .footer { background-color: var(--primary-dark); color: white; text-align: center; padding: 30px 20px; }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .bot-hero-container { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
            .bot-hero-text h1 { font-size: 32px; }
            .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .nav-links { display: none; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .logo { gap: 10px; }
            .logo-icon img { width: 38px; height: 38px; }
            .logo-title { font-size: 20px; }
            .logo-subtitle { font-size: 8px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- 頂部導覽列 -->
    <header class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="index.html" class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon"><img src="images/logopng.png" alt="護胰大聯盟 Logo"></div>
                <div class="logo-text-wrapper">
                    <span class="logo-title">護胰大聯盟</span>
                    <span class="logo-subtitle">PANCREAS PROTECTION ALLIANCE</span>
                </div>
            </a>
            <nav class="nav-links">
                <a href="index.html" class="dropbtn">返回首頁</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- 主視覺介紹區塊 -->
    <section class="bot-hero">
        <div class="bot-hero-container">
            <div class="bot-hero-text">
                <h1>用聊天掌握健康<br>您的專屬 <span>AI 護胰管家</span></h1>
                <p>我們收錄了國民健康署、衛生福利部以及全台各大醫學中心的胰臟疾病衛教知識。<br>省去繁瑣的網頁搜尋步驟，只要打開 LINE，強大的 AI 將隨時為您解答有關胰臟健康的任何問題！</p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px;">
                    <span style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 8px 15px; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 14px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">✔️ 免費加入</span>
                    <span style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 8px 15px; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 14px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">✔️ 24小時在線</span>
                    <span style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 8px 15px; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 14px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">✔️ 權威醫療資料庫</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="qr-card-wrapper">
                <div class="qr-card">
                    <!-- 請確認 images 資料夾中有這張裁切好的 line_qr.png -->
                    <img src="images/line_qr.png" alt="掃描加入護胰大聯盟 LINE">
                    <h3>護胰大聯盟</h3>
                    <div class="bot-id">ID: @996fwyab</div>
                    <!-- 手機用戶點擊按鈕可直接開啟 LINE 加入好友 -->
                    <a href="https://line.me/R/ti/p/@996fwyab" class="btn-line-add">加入 LINE 好友</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 功能特色區塊 -->
    <section class="features-section">
        <h2 class="features-title">為什麼要使用官方 LINE？</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <span class="feature-icon">🤖</span>
                <h3>AI 語意理解，對答如流</h3>
                <p>不需要記指令或點選複雜的選單。您可以像和醫生朋友聊天一樣，直接用口語發問，AI 會自動理解您的問題並給予精準回覆。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <span class="feature-icon">🏛️</span>
                <h3>來源權威，安心可靠</h3>
                <p>所有 AI 回答的基礎，皆建構於衛福部、國健署及各大醫院的最新衛教資料庫。我們為您過濾網路農場文，確保您獲得的是最正確的醫療常識。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <span class="feature-icon">📱</span>
                <h3>零門檻，長輩也能輕鬆用</h3>
                <p>無需額外下載 App，更不用學會複雜的網頁操作。只要平時會使用 LINE 傳訊息，就能隨時隨地進行風險評估與知識查詢。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 頁尾 -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <p style="margin-bottom: 5px; color: white;"><strong>護胰大聯盟 PANCREAS PROTECTION ALLIANCE</strong></p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin: 0;">
                © 2026 仲智數位健康 (PanCAD.ai). All Rights Reserved. | 
                <a href="privacy.html" target="_blank" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-decoration: underline;">隱私權政策</a> | 
                <a href="terms.html" target="_blank" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-decoration: underline;">服務條款</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>